Calc assumes full c20 with kzarka, heve, +3 dg. Only c15 dande, so add 2 if you care about awakened.

Stats include alch stone but no other buffs. Normal crystal setup

Select current accessories from the dropdown and press input gear -- ONLY IF THEY ARE PEN, IF NOT LEAVE AT NONE

If none is selected, assumes tet accessories - disto, basi, tungrad ring, ogre, vell, just in terms of how much they would sell for in order to cover cost of buying pen

Prices used:

Griffon is set to 60b cost as it assumes you start with heve, if you already have c20 then subtract 60b from the total.

 itemPrices.insert("Disto", 100);
